# Core Boundaries

- Respect layer direction: `ui -> engine` and `render -> engine`, never reverse.
- Keep `src/engine/**` pure and independent from UI, render, and browser APIs.
- Prefer imports from `*/public.ts` entrypoints; avoid deep cross-layer imports.
- Do not introduce circular imports.
- Keep game logic inside engine systems; render loop only syncs visuals.
- Keep Zustand for UI/debug/sim controls only, never per-frame ECS entity data.
- Use named exports only; no default exports.
